produts.name: Calabrese Broccoli
produts.description: Calabrese broccoli, also known as broccoli romanesco, is a type of broccoli that is native to Italy. It is characterized by its tightly packed, spiraled florets that resemble a miniature Romanesque cathedral.

produts.name: Vegan Red Tomato
produts.description: Vegan red tomatoes are a type of tomato that is grown without the use of any animal products. This includes fertilizers, pesticides, and herbicides. Vegan tomatoes are also typically picked when they are ripe, which means that they are more flavorful and nutritious than non-vegan tomatoes.

produts.name: Mung Bean
produts.description: Mung beans, also known as green gram beans, are a type of legume that is native to India and Southeast Asia. They are a small, green bean that is about the size of a lentil. Mung beans are a good source of protein, fiber, and vitamins and minerals. They are also low in calories and fat.
